Package: pghelpers
Title: Helper Functions for Allegheny County Property Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jimmy", "Hogan", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helper functions for loading property assessment data from
    Western Pennsylvania Regional Data Center (WPRDC) APIs. Includes functions
    for loading condemned properties, assessment appeals, and other property-related
    datasets.
